    <!-- http://www.smolang.org/bedreflyt/Bed -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.smolang.org/bedreflyt/Bed">
        <rdfs:comment>This could come from REC or BRICKS, it is a subclass of Furniture there. However, I would consider it medical equipment, given that these beds have medical functionality (lots of buttoms and special properties that make them more than furniture). So, therefore I do not import from REC.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>ref to REC &lt;https://w3id.org/rec&gt;:589:14</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Class>
    


